{"tid":1057204,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍銀座間「泰妹」好撚垃圾","createTime":"2019-03-11T17:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T03:41:21.000Z","uid":35644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6def0f907ed39472e7f6e73699a54e904f5ab7","tid":1057204,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"我一枱人嗌左超過10樣野食 除左生蝦之外 其餘基本上狗也不屌 <br />\n<br />\n海南雞鞋到好似擦膠咁 仲要凍冰冰 明顯啱啱係雪櫃拎出黎 個飯只係染左黃色嘅冷飯 食到差啲想嘔<br />\n<br />\n串燒鹹到仆街 食完一串之後飲左兩杯水<br />\n<br />\n炒麵炒飯可以冇味嘅 以為自己食緊齋<br />\n<br />\n咖喱包入面浸到淋晒 好似食緊濕撚晒嘅發脹麵包咁<br />\n<br />\n小食拼盤仲衰撚過街市小食店 油到仆街 仲要燶鳩晒<br />\n<br />\n飲品又係搵笨 廿幾蚊一杯熱飲 柒到用普通水杯裝 仲要難飲到仆街<br />\n<br />\n另外最撚on9係個餐牌 屌你老母整到咁撚大塊把撚呀? 張枱又唔係大 阻撚住晒 設計個條柒頭快啲死撚左佢啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CY5ZEZS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCY5ZEZS.jpg&h=b4a46cf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bcc375a3f1243eb98e1e7f9109cdb7177c5d1ff","tid":1057204,"uid":23120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1c11c026ab8afd02c9ce673422822214459c74","tid":1057204,"uid":23120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:37:10.000Z","msg":"依間即係t town亞萊泰個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a9809f2210ced20f5fc67c1a1880fc8994503f","tid":1057204,"uid":82398,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"食物相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無既話我會認為係同行攻擊對手？"},{"pid":"f143a34eb41c50f2acd19669cf48d13c625fda9b","tid":1057204,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"真係食泰妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.g